text: It's alright look, in that light!
--as soon as I put it on the line  --
It's alright in this light, look!
God I haven't got many bloody skirts or anything!
Well I don't understand what it is  --
--don't know why you really needed it!
You didn't have a tissue up it did you?
You had a tissue up that!
You had a tissue up it, in there!
Cos you do agree with me it is?
I suppose it means buying you one now doesn't it?
I told you when you emptied the pockets  (())
Yeah, but I get the bla- bloody blame for it then!
And that's the only sweatshirt I've got!
The tissue, look what you've done to it!
I know what I've done to it!
I've got one jumper, one sweatshirt!
I'll get it off if you'll shut up!
--you know I'm not very good at bloody washing anyway!
